   </blockquote> <h3>
    <!--mstheme--><font color="#CC0000">Creating a web page on your school's site
     <!--mstheme--></font></h3> 
   <blockquote> 
    <p>Be sure to include "meta" statements within your html &lt;head&gt; area so that the browsers will automatically update to show the latest helicorder record.&nbsp; As an example, look at the html source code for my station:&nbsp; <a href="heli/chor.html">College Hill, Corvallis, Oregon</a>.</p> 
    <p>&lt;<span class="start-tag">meta</span><span class="attribute-name"> http-equiv</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"Refresh" </span> <span class="attribute-name">content</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"600"</span>&gt;<br> &lt;<span class="start-tag">meta</span><span class="attribute-name"> http-equiv</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"pragma" </span><span class="attribute-name">content</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"no-cache"</span>&gt;<br> &lt;<span class="start-tag">meta</span><span class="attribute-name"> http-equiv</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"expires" </span><span class="attribute-name">content</span>=<span class="attribute-value">"-1"</span>&gt;</p> 
   </blockquote> <h3>
